Diamond Chandbali Pendant - Adhunik Chandbali Bottu

₹168,917

Description

This pendant is a unique blend of tradition and contemporary design. The Chandbali motif has cultural significance, symbolizing femininity and prosperity. The brilliant-cut diamonds provide unparalleled sparkle, and the rose gold setting offers a modern and romantic appeal. The Hyderabadi polish ensures a lasting luster.

Materials

  • 18K Rose Gold
  • Brilliant Cut Diamonds (Color: G-H
  • Clarity: VS)
  • Hyderabadi Polish

Features

A contemporary take on the traditional Chandbali design, this pendant features a crescent moon shape adorned with teardrop accents. The entire piece is encrusted with shimmering brilliant cut diamonds in a pave setting, maximizing brilliance. The rose gold finish adds warmth and a modern touch.
